## Out of Scope (Deferred)

These items from the feedback are valuable but require deeper changes:
- **QR code generation** — Needs a QR library dependency; can be added later
- **Version/revision marker on PDF** — Needs passing revision count into template data from the API
- **Trust badges** (GST-compliant, Secure payment) — These are cosmetic additions that can be layered on after core improvements
- **Mobile-first readability checks** — The link page is already responsive; PDF is A4-fixed

> [!NOTE]
> These deferred items are all good ideas and can be picked up in a follow-up iteration.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Run the dev server and navigate to an existing proposal's public link (`/view/[id]`) to verify:
  - Scope Snapshot card renders correctly
  - Next Steps action block appears under total
  - Footer is simplified
- Navigate to an invoice page (`/invoice/[id]`) to verify footer simplification
- The PDF templates can be verified by checking the HTML output structure in the template code (actual PDF generation requires Browserless.io)
